Miscellaneous utilities, like ASCII table formatters and precodition checkers

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ParameterizedRunnable<R,T>
    Abstraction barrier used to call methods behind the run method
    Row
    The interface that represents a horizontal row on the ASCII table
    SerializableRunnable<V>
    A runnable that can be serialized.
  • Class Summary

    Checks
    Shortcut methods to throw exceptions if condition is not met

    Represents a row of data on the ASCII table
    Table
    ASCII table wrapper that can be formatted and printed out to the console
